subject: Hockey, Ice
Playoff Games
Stanley Cup
lead_paragraph: Henrik Sedin scored with 1 minute 54 seconds left in the fourth overtime to lift the Canucks to a 5-4 victory over the Dallas Stars on Wednesday night.
